ed="T" n="0842b26"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0842b26"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000019682"><placeName>洪州</placeName><placeName>黃蘗山</placeName></placeName><persName key="A000490">希運</persName><ptr rend="display:none;" target="#n2670"/>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0842b27"/><persName key="A000490">釋希運</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000017165">閩</placeName>人也<ptr target="#n2672"/>。年及就<anchor xml:id="beg0842003"/>傅<anchor xml:id="end0842003"/>，鄉校推其慧利。<lb
ed="T" n="0842b28"/>乃割愛投<placeName key="PL000000019688"><placeName>高安</placeName><placeName>黃蘗山寺</placeName></placeName>出家<ptr target="#n2673"/>。迨成長也，<lb
ed="T" n="0842b29"/>身量減<persName key="A019454">王商</persName>裁一尺所<ptr target="#n2671"/>，額間隆起，號為「肉<pb ed="T" n="0842c" xml:id="T50.2061.0842c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0842c01"/>珠」。然倜儻不羈，人莫輕測。而乃觀方入<placeName key="PL000000014411">天<lb
ed="T" n="0842c02"/>台</placeName>，偶逢一僧偕行，言笑自若。<persName key="A000490">運</persName>偷窺之，其<lb
ed="T" n="0842c03"/>目時閃爍，爛然射人。相比而行，截路巨磎，<lb
ed="T" n="0842c04"/>泛泛湧溢，如是捐笠倚杖而止。其僧督<persName key="A000490">運</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0842c05"/>渡去，乃強激發之曰：「師要渡自渡。」言訖，其<lb
ed="T" n="0842c06"/>僧褰衣<ptr type="glossary" target="#g929"/>躡波，若履平陸，曾無沾濕，已到他<lb
ed="T" n="0842c07"/>岸矣。迴顧招手曰：「渡來。」<persName key="A000490">運</persName>戟手<ptr type="glossary" target="#g693"/>呵曰：「咄，自了<lb
ed="T" n="0842c08"/>漢<ptr target="#n2674"/>，早知必<anchor xml:id="beg0842sgsz19"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>斯</sic><corr>斮</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0842sgsz19"/>汝脛。」其僧歎曰：「真大乘法器，我<lb
ed="T" n="0842c09"/>所不及。縱能傷我，只取辱焉。」少頃不見。<persName key="A000490">運</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0842c10"/>𢠵<anchor xml:id="beg0842sgsz21"/>怳<anchor xml:id="end0842sgsz21"/><ptr type="glossary" target="#g1054"/>自失。及薄遊<ptr type="glossary" target="#g674"/><ref type="place" target="#PL000000042189">京闕</ref>，分衛<ptr type="glossary" target="#g602"/>及一家門，屏<lb
ed="T" n="0842c11"/>樹之後聞一姥曰：「太無厭乎？」<persName key="A000490">運</persName>曰：「主不慁<lb
ed="T" n="0842c12"/>賓<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1774"/>，何無厭之有？」姥召入，施食訖。姥曰：「五障<lb
ed="T" n="0842c13"/>之身<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1775"/>忝甞禮<persName key="A001707">惠忠<roleName>國師</roleName></persName>來。勸<ref type="person" target="#A000490">師</ref>可往尋<placeName key="PL000000019628">百<lb
ed="T" n="0842c14"/>丈山</placeName>禪師所，惜巍巍乎堂堂乎真大乘器也。」<lb
ed="T" n="0842c15"/><persName key="A000490">運</persName>念受二過，記莂<ptr target="#n2307"/>攸同，乃還<placeName key="PL000000018628">洪井</placeName>見<persName key="A001897">海<roleName>禪<lb
ed="T" n="0842c16"/>師</roleName></persName><ptr target="#n1895"/>，開了心趣，聲價彌高。徇命居<placeName key="PL000000019688">黃蘗精舍</placeName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0842c17"/>昇平相<persName key="A003624">裴<roleName>公</roleName>休</persName>欽重躬謁，有詩贈焉：「曾傳達<lb
ed="T" n="0842c18"/>士心中印，額有圓珠七尺身。挂錫十年棲<lb
ed="T" n="0842c19"/><placeName key="PL000000059373">蜀水</placeName>，浮盃<ptr target="#n1249"/>今日渡<placeName key="PL000000059374">漳</placeName>濱。一千龍象隨高步，萬<lb
ed="T" n="0842c20"/>里香<anchor xml:id="beg0842sgsz23"/>華<anchor xml:id="end0842sgsz23"/>結勝因。願欲事<persName key="A000490">師</persName>為弟子，不知將<lb
ed="T" n="0842c21"/>法付何<anchor xml:id="beg0842004"/>人<anchor xml:id="end0842004"/>！」<ptr target="#n609"/>則<persName key="A003624">裴<roleName>相</roleName></persName>得法，出<persName key="A000490">運</persName>之門。以<date notBefore-iso="+0847-02-10" key="j20304612035056" notAfter-iso="+0859-09-10"><name>大中</name><lb
ed="T" n="0842c22"/>中</date>終于所住寺，勅謚<persName key="A000490">斷際禪師</persName><ptr target="#n610"/>，塔名<placeName key="PL000000019686">廣業</placeName><ptr target="#n611"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0842c23"/>語錄而行于世。</p>
